text: World of Quest is a Canadianâ€“American animated television series produced by Cookie Jar Group. It appears to be a parody of the fantasy genre that blends swords, sorcery and technology, in the vein of Masters of the Universe. The show had two different stories in each episode. The show was cancelled after only two season of twenty-six episodes. The series premiered airs at 11AM ET/PT time on October 17, 2008 on Cartoon Network in the United States.
